<dl id="n42030c"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n42" href="#n42030c">N42 (VI.B.31)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n42all.htm#n42030c"> 30(c)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> 7 taverns no / school / 7 schools no / tavern</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><font color="green">[BIOGRAPHICAL. WHO IS CHINIQUY? Important Original Documents, establishing the high character and standing of pastor Chiniquy when in the Church of Rome]</font> He began at Beauport, where he was parish priest. There were then seven taverns or hotels, but no school. In two years he had seven schools, and not a single tavern in the parish. <small> Chiniquy, <a name="CPWC" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#CPWC"><cite title="source">The Priest The Woman and The Confessional</cite></a> (n.d.) v</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
